{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_11_01_short",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 そんな光景を見てみたい (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ十月かぁ……\n時が経つのは早いわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's almost October‚ huh…\nTime really flies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5000,
          "startTime": 5.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます、遙子さん\nぼーっとカレンダーを見て、どうかしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Haruko-san.\nYou were staring blankly at the calendar—something on your mind?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、{user}君\n実は、麻奈ちゃんのことを思い出していたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}-kun.\nActually‚ I was thinking about Mana-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ、麻奈ちゃんのお誕生日でしょう？\n今年はどうお祝いしようかなって考えていたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her birthday is coming up soon‚ right?\nI was wondering how to celebrate it this year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。確かにそろそろですよね\n今年もちゃんとお祝いしないとだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Yeah‚ it's about that time.\nWe should make sure to celebrate properly this year too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "みんなに声を掛けて、盛大に……なんてどうかしら？\n麻奈ちゃんも、そっちの方が嬉しいでしょうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What if we invite everyone and make it grand…?\nMana-chan would probably be happier that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いいですね。そういえば、麻奈の誕生日に偶然\n月ストのライブがあるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds good. Come to think of it‚ by coincidence‚\nthere's a Moon Tempest live show on Mana's birthday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃にそのことを伝えたら、「お姉ちゃんをお祝いして\nあげたい」って、追加で一曲、歌うことになりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I told Kotono‚ she said‚ “I want to celebrate my sister‚”\nso she'll be singing an extra song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんから麻奈ちゃんへのプレゼント\nっていうことかしら。素敵な歌になりそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So it'll be Kotono-chan's present to Mana-chan‚ right?\nIt sounds like it'll be a lovely song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}